<h1>Creating Global Keyboard Shortcuts</h1>
</div>
</div>
<!--closes page header-->
<div id="taskbox">

<p>	CoverSutra allows you to set up Key Combinations for a variety of functions to control iTunes. These keyboard Shortcuts are global, so you can use them while working in any application you like.

	Any Key Combination made in the System Preferences application override CoverSutra shortcuts. Try to use a Key Combination that is not already being used.</p>

