</div>
<div class="taskauxoption">
<div class="taskauxcontent">
<li>
<p class="textlistnumber"><strong>To define a Shortcut:</strong> Click into the Shortcut Recorder Control and type in the Key Combination you would like to use.<br/><strong>To remove:</strong> Click the small gray close button on the Shortcut Recorder Control.</p>
</li>

</div>
</div>
</ol><!--closes taskauxlistnumbered-->
<p>Note: You can disable all shortcuts by choosing Disable Shortcuts from the status item menu.</p>
